至翌日下午5時)致電本會1817登記</span><br />\n<br />\n我反而想知<br />\n點解預得 幾個鐘畀人做登記<br />\n唔按時登記會點?"},{"pid":"6458e6c2d1c780fe08f03c5310445d9fa7aa18c7","tid":2352530,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1851f6fc3e024b76d0049981b4d7c514e0f37752","tid":2352530,"uid":34530,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"傻佬，用app 買完張飛 numbers 會轉，一定唔會中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"我真係有擔心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c59970118f7b919cd53da819a3f131898f72c3c","tid":2352530,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"依家馬會有冇開門<br />\n想開網上戶口<br />\n睇下手風<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7456a5e9e81fdb9808f6aba9e3a4ef2fcffffde7","tid":2352530,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c59970118f7b919cd53da819a3f131898f72c3c","tid":2352530,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"依家馬會有冇開門<br />\n想開網上戶口<br />\n睇下手風<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"指定分店同時間有開<br />\n上網自己check"},{"pid":"bb5f2711963300b681a19de09304cfa1202cae67","tid":2352530,"uid":175523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"超過五百萬元獎金之中獎登記新安排<br />\n<br />\n2015年2月23日<br />\n<br />\n本會將於明日(2月24日)起，就十元一注超過五百萬元的公佈獎金之中獎登記，實施新的安排。<br />\n<br />\n所有透過互動投注服務進行投注的中獎者，將毋須向本會登記，有關獎金會自動存入其投注戶口內#。互動投注服務包括網上投注服務「投注區」、流動投注服務、Racing Touch流動應用程式、電訊運財寶及投注寶。<br />\n<br />\n而使用現金投注或透過電話投注服務(包括1886電話投注自動服務系統)、智財咭及「固定指示」服務投注的中獎登記安排，將維持不變，中獎者仍須於指定時間致電馬會熱線1817登記。<br />\n<br />\n#有關獎金將於六合彩攪珠日或賽馬日的翌日下午五時後存入中獎者之投注戶口。<br />\n<br />\n* 投注人士必須年滿十八歲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-02/news_2015022301511.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fcorporate%2Fracing_news_item.asp%3Fin_file%3D%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2015-02%2Fnews_2015022301511.html&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=9015d3b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-02/news_2015022301511.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b0bd673960a39de070a1e459c9eb34589a88583","tid":2352530,"uid":30351,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"咪痴撚線啦<br />\n馬會一年袋咁多<br />\n點會咁呃你呀<br />\n開賭唔怕你贏<br />\n最怕你唔黎賭<br />\n唔公道既搵鬼黎賭"},{"pid":"33db5979d025d3f3d10ddf73ce2f88f0fbc829bb","tid":2352530,"uid":275498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb5f2711963300b681a19de09304cfa1202cae67","tid":2352530,"uid":175523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"超過五百萬元獎金之中獎登記新安排<br />\n<br />\n2015年2月23日<br />\n<br />\n本會將於明日(2月24日)起，就十元一注超過五百萬元的公佈獎金之中獎登記，實施新的安排。<br />\n<br />\n所有透過互動投注服務進行投注的中獎者，將毋須向本會登記，有關獎金會自動存入其投注戶口內#。互動投注服務包括網上投注服務「投注區」、流動投注服務、Racing Touch流動應用程式、電訊運財寶及投注寶。<br />\n<br />\n而使用現金投注或透過電話投注服務(包括1886電話投注自動服務系統)、智財咭及「固定指示」服務投注的中獎登記安排，將維持不變，中獎者仍須於指定時間致電馬會熱線1817登記。<br />\n<br />\n#有關獎金將於六合彩攪珠日或賽馬日的翌日下午五時後存入中獎者之投注戶口。<br />\n<br />\n* 投注人士必須年滿十八歲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-02/news_2015022301511.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fcorporate%2Fracing_news_item.asp%3Fin_file%3D%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2015-02%2Fnews_2015022301511.html&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=9015d3b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2015-02/news_2015022301511.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  pin this !"},{"